{"tid":347112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★逾七千市民反對興建公屋！","createTime":"2017-08-04T13:42:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-04T15:29:10.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3fb90e0ccd76462d526cd600fbc4370a4fdbe1d3","tid":347112,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T13:42:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">逾七千市民反對　宏照道建公屋計劃觸礁</span><br />\n<br />\n房屋署建公屋計劃又觸礁，九龍灣宏照道擬建5幢公屋，提供4100個單位，城市規劃委員會收到8460份申述，絕大部分是反對計劃。有建議把東九龍文化中心遷至宏照道用地，並將牛頭角下邨的原址用來興建公屋。<br />\n<br />\n宏照道公屋計劃分兩期進行，第一期擬建3座約40層高公屋，單位數目約2650個，房署如意算盤是2018年開工，2023年落成。<br />\n<br />\n不過，城規會收到大量反對意見，當中觀塘區議員簡銘東、馬軼超、謝淑珍、黃子健、鄭景陽和九龍城區議員何華漢，聯同7000多名市民提交意見。他們建議維持原先規劃，保留新秀大廈，讓勵行會繼續使用，而勵行會可與第一期公屋共存，但撤回第二期。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170804/bkn-20170804193317078-0804_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170804%2Fbkn-20170804193317078-0804_00822_001.html&d=YH7RNHwbniSxePq9ahxhmfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=1c786840\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170804/bkn-20170804193317078-0804_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b7984e7ac6c160fb40354bd2c85712f00b11d137","tid":347112,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T13:43:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 地產狗"},{"pid":"a488c786ed662a431f93ebe699c8a9d92ec2ce73","tid":347112,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T13:44:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大量反對意見，當中觀塘區議員簡銘東、馬軼超、謝淑珍、黃子健、鄭景陽和九龍城區議員何華漢，聯同7000多名市民</span>"},{"pid":"65cd9a5424e2884012b6869e7173ef9082654caa","tid":347112,"uid":25952,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-0